LORE SUCCESS!!! This looks like it was originally made to be a crypt or burial chamber. In 1239DR, the Year of the Bloodied Sword, over two hundred firbolg overran the cantrevs of Koart and O'Malley before being slaughtered by the warriors of Corwell. You wonder if the people of Koart know that they are storing their meat where members of the MacKorart clan used to be laid to rest... but perhaps their commerce-minded Laird does not care about such relics of the past.
